PATCH = browser/${NAME}.patch
TITLE = Auto Hide All Icons After Page Load
DESCRIPTION = Hides all icons except the loading icon when the browser app is loading/refreshing page.<br/><br/>For those with Flash:<br/>Once you click on Flash Content, the X to close out of it will appear. After you click the X, it icon will go away.
